  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop the<strong> red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\n<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>\n<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p>\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped onion</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>dried chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 3-4 min or until softened</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2252.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2252.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2252.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2252.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2252.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p>\n<p>Add the<strong> linguine</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>\n<p>Cook the <strong>linguine</strong> for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p>\n<p>Once done, drain the <strong>linguine</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2252.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2252.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2252.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2252.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2252.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the linguine is cooking, add the <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> and <strong>tomato paste</strong> to the pan with the <strong>softened onion</strong> and stir it all together</p>\n<p>Season with a grind of<strong> black</strong> <strong>pepper</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2252.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2252.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2252.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2252.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2252.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the skin from the<strong> smoked mackerel fillets</strong></p>\n<p>Tip: Watch out for any tiny bones and discard them</p>\n<p>Tear the <strong>smoked mackerel</strong> into rough pieces </p>\n<p>Slice the<strong> black olives</strong> finely</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2252.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2252.-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
