            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Crumble 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>Knorr vegetable stock cube </strong>into the pan and add a couple of splashes of <strong>starchy pasta water</strong> </p>\n<p>Give everything a stir, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 5-6 min or until a thick pasta sauce remains</p>",
